OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FAn "affluent" and "well brought-up"
OL,7,Fdrug user stabbed his mother to death
OL,8,Foutside their family home in the
OL,9,Fpresence of his father, a murder trial
OL,10,Fjury was told.
OL,12,FThe court heard Gregor Bauld was 22
OL,13,Fyears old when he murdered his mother
OL,14,FChristine Bauld in the street outside
OL,15,Ftheir house in The Coppice in Burbage,
OL,16,FLeicestershire, on March 3.
