OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FBauld, now 23, pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmanslaughter and denied murder on the
OL,8,Fgrounds of diminished responsibility
OL,9,Fat Leicester Crown Court on Wednesday,
OL,10,Fbut a jury will be asked to decide
OL,11,Fbased on the evidence whether he is
OL,12,Fguilty of the more serious offence of
OL,13,Fmurder.
OL,15,FThe defendant sat in the dock while
OL,16,FGordon Aspden KC, prosecuting, opened
OL,17,Fthe case and said Mrs Bauld, 55, was
OL,18,F"defenceless" in the attack after she
OL,19,Fwas chased out of the four-bedroom
OL,20,Fdetached house by her son.
