OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FMr Aspden said: "This case involves an
OL,7,Fallegation that the defendant murdered
OL,8,Fhis mother Christine Bauld, or Tina as
OL,9,Fshe was known, by stabbing her to
OL,10,Fdeath with a kitchen knife in the
OL,11,Fstreet in the presence of his father,
OL,12,Fher husband.
OL,14,F"The Crown's case is that on the
OL,15,Fmorning of Sunday March 3 of this
OL,16,Fyear, the defendant murdered his
OL,17,Fmother by attacking and stabbing her
OL,18,Fto death outside their family house."
