OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FMr Aspden continues: "He admits he
OL,7,Fkilled his mother unlawfully and is
OL,8,Fguilty of manslaughter, but denies
OL,9,Fthat what he did amounts to the more
OL,10,Fserious crime of murder.
OL,12,F"He was a well brought-up young man
OL,13,Fwith two loving parents who lived in a
OL,14,Fcomfortable and relatively affluent
OL,15,Fhome environment.
OL,17,F"However, as he got older and entered
OL,18,Fhis early teens, his life became
OL,19,Fblighted by chronic drug abuse and
OL,20,Fassociated mental health problems."
