OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FThe court was told that Bauld started
OL,7,Fusing drugs when he was aged 13 or 14.
OL,9,FThe prosecutor said paramedics arrived
OL,10,Fat the scene at 11.19 that morning
OL,11,Fwhere Mrs Bauld was in cardiac arrest
OL,12,Fand underwent emergency surgery "on
OL,13,Fthe concrete" but was pronounced dead
OL,14,F37 minutes later.
OL,16,FMr Aspden told the jury a pathologist
OL,17,Fdetermined Mrs Bauld's cause of death
OL,18,Fas a stab wound to the back which
OL,19,Fpenetrated the blood vessels supplying
OL,20,Fblood to her heart.
