OL,3,C'Well brought-up' drug user murdered
OL,4,Cmother outside family home, court told
OL,6,FHe added that Bauld's father, who held
OL,7,Fhis wife in his arms after the attack,
OL,8,Fwas "severely traumatised" and in a
OL,9,F"state of obvious shock".
OL,11,FPolice recovered a knife with a 12.5-
OL,12,Finch blade in the family's kitchen
OL,13,Fwith "apparent blood staining", the
OL,14,Fcourt was told.
OL,16,FThe defendant is alleged to have
OL,17,Fanswered the door to police officers
OL,18,Ffollowing the attack and appeared
OL,19,F"calm" and "somewhat subdued".
