OL,6,FMr Aspden told the court that the
OL,7,Fdefendant had been "in the grip of a
OL,8,Fdestructive cycle of drug abuse"
OL,9,Fleading up to the incident, and that
OL,10,Fblood and urine samples showed
OL,11,F"striking" traces of drugs, including
OL,12,FLSD and ketamine.
OL,14,FThe trial continues.
